1 bunch baby broccoli
1 packet firm tofu
1 sachet Sweet Soy Seasoning
1 packet Plum Sauce
1 packet Microwavable Basmati Rice
1 bag coriander
1 packet Crushed Peanuts
1 bag Asian Stir-Fry Mix
olive oil

• Chop baby broccoli into thirds
• Drain tofu and cut into 2cm chunks

• Heat olive oil in a frying pan over
high heat
• Cook baby broccoli, tofu and sweet
soy seasoning until tender, 4-5 mins
• Add Asian stir-fry mix and cook until
wilted, 1-2 mins
• Remove the pan from heat and add
plum sauce

• Meanwhile, zap rice in microwave
until steaming, 2-3 mins
• Plate up rice and top with
tofu stir-fry
• Top with torn coriander and peanuts